        public void deleteCustomer​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
                    throws java.io.IOException
        This method takes the selected customer from the customer table and deletes them after clicking OK on the confirmation alert. If there are any appointments attached to the customer, the user will receive an alert of said appointments. Once confirmed, the data is deleted from the table and the database.
